ANNOUNCEMENT 📣 
We have teamed up with our friends @fishingtobeatcc @beatchildhoodcancer to help the fight.  Everyone knows someone that cancer has affected.  Our hearts go out to all of the families that have children fighting cancer and we want to support any way that we can.  Please watch this video and share with anyone that might be interested in this amazing 25 bay with everything over $212k going directly to the children of @beatchildhoodcancer.  The MSRP is $266k and the wait is over a year on a new bay boat.  Who wants to join us and use this as a write off for your taxes?  It’s a win win for everyone.
